      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant should be a resident of the Union territory of Andaman &amp;amp; Nicobar Islands.\n   1. The applicant should be engaged in any building &amp;amp; other construction work.\n   1. The applicant should be registered under the A&amp;amp;N Islands Building and Other Construction Workers Welfare Board.\n   1. The applicant should have an active membership of the Board.\n   1. The son or daughter of the applicant/registered worker should be enrolled in any grade from Class I to Post Graduate Level/Professional Course.\n\n",
